  Don Jazzy has taken to his social media to show his fans alternative ways to use the toilet now to avoid being bitten by a snake. This is coming after a viral news of a woman who died after a large venomous snake bit her as she sat on the toilet. The woman, who worked for the Nigerian Air Force and has been identified as Lance Corporal Ogah Bercy, was rushed to hospital but was pronounced dead on arrival. READ ALSO: Don Jazzy & other Nigerian celebrities react to video of taxi driver being pepper-strayed by security operatives (video) Many Nigerians have reacted to the news and some have been really cautions before they use the toilet. Don Jazzy on the other hand shared an hilarious video of how he will be using the toilet He said: “Finding alternative ways to sh*t ooo. This thing is not funny anymore.”   A post shared by ITS DON JAZZY AGAIN (@donjazzy)    